---
### URL Syntax

Used syntax: `https://img.shields.io/badge/` + `<left text>` + `-` + `<right text>` + `-` + `<right text background color>` + `?logo=` + `<base64 image>`, where 
- `<left text>` is for example `LabVIEW`,
- `<right text>` is for example `21.1_(32--bit)` (note that `_` is replaced with `<space>` and `--` with `-`),
- `<right text background color>` is for example `FFC500`,
- `<base64 image>` is Base64 image generated out of SVG file using [Base64 Guru](https://base64.guru/converter/encode/image/svg), using _Data URI_ output format.
